                        Products Products     Product The ULTRALAST® TPU portfolio is composed of high quality products based on a variety of chemistries, all with the unique composition derived from low free monomer (LF) technology. All grades offer processing advantages of lower processing temperatures, reduced cycle times, improved thermal stability, easier demolding and better aesthetics compared to standard TPUs and other high performance specialty elastomers.The M-Series elastomers are resistant to hydrolysis and extremely tough with high cut and tear resistance and superior dynamic properties. They are ideal for use in low temperature applications, down to -80˚C.The P-Series elastomers are designed for the most demanding applications. They offer superior toughness, excellent dynamic properties and can perform consistently at elevated temperatures up to 165˚C and in harsh chemical environments.The H-Series elastomers provide excellent weatherability, UV resistance and color retention, while offering high rebound, toughness with high cut and tear resistance, and low temperature performance.PRODUCTS








